{"tid":1847441,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一頁有懶人包]網購外科口罩集中討論23","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T13:53:09.000Z","uid":24904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a33ef63adc86336a60f8128721f755b9a14e52cf","tid":1847441,"uid":24904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ref: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kkfly.hk/posts/573240539893484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkkfly.hk%2Fposts%2F573240539893484%2F&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=22c85dbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kkfly.hk/posts/573240539893484/</a><br />\n如何揀口罩<br />\n<br />\n背景：武漢沙士 -&gt; 冠狀病毒<br />\n跟據網上資料，2003年SARS既病毒大小係0.08-0.14&mu;m<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==現時有既standard==<br />\n1. BFE= Bacteria Filtration Efficiency = 細菌阻隔率(樣本大小: 3&mu;m, 容許: 1-5&mu;m)<br />\n結論： 得BFE冇用，因為唔夠細<br />\n<br />\n2. PFE = Particle Filtration Efficiency = 顆粒阻隔率(樣本大小: 0.1&mu;m)<br />\n結論：因為飛沫最細只係去到0.6&mu;m，所以夠用<br />\nPS: 醫護用會上到呢個standard。如果你相信政府，佢係飛抹傳染而唔會空氣傳染既話<br />\n<br />\n3. VFE = Virus Filtration Efficiency = 病毒阻隔率(樣本大小: 0.1-5&mu;m, 載體: phiX 174)<br />\n暫時最勁既standard, according to Nelson lab 可以隔到0.027微米<br />\n呢個size防到舊沙士既virus有突<br />\n我暫時只見到日本某d口罩做到<br />\n<br />\n==結論==<br />\nPFE &gt; VFE &gt; BFE<br />\n強 &gt; 弱<br />\n基本上有PFE 另外個兩種都防到<br />\n日本野：最少要見到PFE+BFE先好買, 得BFE唔好買，冇用<br />\n寫清楚有齊PFE+BFE+VFE當然最好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ULUsfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ULUsfj.jpg&h=c0ac2f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==阻隔標準==<br />\n歐洲: EN14683 (得BFE，無PFE標準)<br />\n美國: ASTM-F2100 lv 1-3 (3最高)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8AQrM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8AQrM3.png&h=589cbb7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2018 standard)<br />\n<br />\n日本: 日本政府網站提出的VFE測試方法係用~1.7&mu;m嘅濾菌體去測試<br />\n比PFE測試所用粒子要大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqBwecB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqBwecB.jpg&h=6ec9152b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國: KF80/94/99 (99最高)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxcvrLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxcvrLk.png&h=1f22814f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣: CNS14774<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUcy9dF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUcy9dF.png&h=59a4c186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2018 standard)<br />\n<br />\n3M:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ENrv5k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ENrv5k.jpg&h=cb64da11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街邊藥房既口罩<br />\n英文既有ASTM Level就係正版啦<br />\n日文既就睇下有冇BFE+PFE+VFE<br />\n冇上面呢兩樣野是但一樣，或者啲日文/英文錯grammar既100%係假野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==其他類型口罩==<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2549572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2549572&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=094d54a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2549572</a><br />\nN95 -<br />\n1860/1860S/1870屬於醫療用口罩，經NIOSH（美國國家職業安全衛生研究所）認證，亦是FDA（美國食品藥品管理局）批准可用作外科手術口罩，有效阻隔效病毒的飛沫。<br />\n8210/8110/9210屬於工業用口罩，主要用於阻隔塵埃，雖然亦經過NIOSH認證，但沒有FDA認可，未必能有效阻隔飛沫。<br />\nPS 1: 同埋醫護有做fit test,確保冇air leak先戴得, 漏氣既話=冇用, 所以我唔建議一般人買 因為好焗(香港隻NASK就ok既 搭飛機可以用 但貴)<br />\n<br />\n防塵/防花粉口罩 -<br />\n冇用架咪on9啦<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴/其他唔係一次性既口罩<br />\n- 首先你要學識點樣正確除豬嘴<br />\n- 仲要唔知你識唔識洗<br />\n- 唔識洗既會contaminate埋你洗衣機d衫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==產地問題==<br />\n大牌子黎講其實大部分made in china<br />\n因為成本問題，醫管局都好多mic野<br />\n但大廠會有qc，所以quality唔會話爭好多<br />\n<br />\n冇經濟能力，搵唔到既<br />\nMade in china都可以照用<br />\n（用日本黎計made in japan個價係mic 4倍)<br />\n<br />\n邊度有得買？<br />\n去屈人寺,萬寧,donki,cosmo搵下啦<br />\n搵唔到就amazon<br />\n但由於日本野唔送海外 所以自己搞轉運啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==牌子問題==<br />\nRef 1: 香港消委會2017-12口罩測試報告 <a href=\"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/f/article/2256/494_p14-21a.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fechoice.consumer.org.hk%2Ff%2Farticle%2F2256%2F494_p14-21a.pdf&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=3dcc57fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/f/article/2256/494_p14-21a.pdf</a><br />\nRef 2: <a href=\"https://tw.tokyocreative.com/articles/30908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.tokyocreative.com%2Farticles%2F30908&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=891baac4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.tokyocreative.com/articles/30908</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 超立體<br />\n超立體嘅口罩係無鐵線的, 除咗一包七個嗰隻係有nose cut之外, 其他全部都冇, 戴眼鏡有機會會起霧, 但係PFE VFE BFE數據一樣99%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">！！要注意呢隻超立體係唔得嘅！！好多人中伏</span><br />\n呢款超立體只有一層, 除咗呢隻，超立體其他款都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjRLMDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjRLMDd.jpg&h=c5c9e2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面呢隻手術用(サージカルタイプ)資料不詳，冇鐵線，有巴打話係醫療用，亦都有人話唔夠三層，可以嘅話就盡量買返另外嘅款喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vK414pX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvK414pX.jpg&h=f4e4f260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 超快適<br />\n無PFE，得VFE，所以唔係所有款都得<br />\n<br />\n3. 三次元<br />\n日本製，全部Ok<br />\n<br />\n4. BMC<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pgf8RN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pgf8RN.jpg&h=15f6d1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. iris<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uCSUmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uCSUmr.jpg&h=1bb4177a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻冇寫數據 可免則免<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdiR9UV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdiR9UV.jpg&h=f4adf87a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. Made In China<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiO6v5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiO6v5d.jpg&h=609c02b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消委會前幾年test過最好表現，好嘢黎<br />\n不過要注意產地係中國，如果好concern就自行判斷喇<br />\n<br />\n7. <strong>Medicom</strong><br />\n政府醫院都係用medicom ASTM level 1<br />\n<br />\n8. <strong>HALYARD</strong><br />\n可以用，醫療級<br />\n<br />\n9. <strong>誠哥有售</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Htgoyoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtgoyoi.jpg&h=84d7f7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係多人買咗嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">伏嘢</span></span><br />\nFrom 阿里巴巴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aY7CCLq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaY7CCLq.png&h=b52492db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3Q</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3qXCLy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3qXCLy.jpg&h=faa59456&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGn7fxe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGn7fxe.jpg&h=51fa0e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國本土個test都係得kf80<br />\n即係得防塵冇防菌<br />\n佢只係做過bfe test但冇show過數字出黎<br />\n<br />\n韓國隻3Q Premium/Premium Plus係冇喺Ministry of Food and Drug Safety(식품의약품안전처) 取得許可 (의약외품허가Drug Approval System)，佢隻KF80/94就有<br />\n不過有巴打話係大陸公司，但唔肯定係唔係真，呢個大家就自行判斷<br />\n<br />\n隔離post睇到：<br />\n千祈唔好買一款叫救救マスク嘅口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837620\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvATVLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvATVLU.jpg&h=570b0a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國製劣質口罩<br />\n<br />\n因為口罩真係有好多好多牌子，如果以上嘅口罩標纖又無mark，呢個post又無巴絲提起過，個樣又流流地，建議大家買過盒啦，唔好為百幾蚊拎自己條命較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貼森林link請加密<br />\n或者淨係貼網址後面嗰抽number<br />\n唔好益CD-ROM</blockquote>"},{"pid":"94b3e32cbcd4cf0532dbcb6d19c6313a130add98","tid":1847441,"uid":206210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123639213b74646591e15a04204e4e2d770cccfb","tid":1847441,"uid":24904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b3e32cbcd4cf0532dbcb6d19c6313a130add98","tid":1847441,"uid":206210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"[第一頁有懶人包]網購外科口罩集中討論23<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847439</a><br />\n<br />\n開慢左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3eeb19ff695cc6ec56a305bb546f6ac738d0810","tid":1847441,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a33ef63adc86336a60f8128721f755b9a14e52cf","tid":1847441,"uid":24904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ref: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kkfly.hk/posts/573240539893484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkkfly.hk%2Fposts%2F573240539893484%2F&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=22c85dbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kkfly.hk/posts/573240539893484/</a><br />\n如何揀口罩<br />\n<br />\n背景：武漢沙士 -&gt; 冠狀病毒<br />\n跟據網上資料，2003年SARS既病毒大小係0.08-0.14&mu;m<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==現時有既standard==<br />\n1. BFE= Bacteria Filtration Efficiency = 細菌阻隔率(樣本大小: 3&mu;m, 容許: 1-5&mu;m)<br />\n結論： 得BFE冇用，因為唔夠細<br />\n<br />\n2. PFE = Particle Filtration Efficiency = 顆粒阻隔率(樣本大小: 0.1&mu;m)<br />\n結論：因為飛沫最細只係去到0.6&mu;m，所以夠用<br />\nPS: 醫護用會上到呢個standard。如果你相信政府，佢係飛抹傳染而唔會空氣傳染既話<br />\n<br />\n3. VFE = Virus Filtration Efficiency = 病毒阻隔率(樣本大小: 0.1-5&mu;m, 載體: phiX 174)<br />\n暫時最勁既standard, according to Nelson lab 可以隔到0.027微米<br />\n呢個size防到舊沙士既virus有突<br />\n我暫時只見到日本某d口罩做到<br />\n<br />\n==結論==<br />\nPFE &gt; VFE &gt; BFE<br />\n強 &gt; 弱<br />\n基本上有PFE 另外個兩種都防到<br />\n日本野：最少要見到PFE+BFE先好買, 得BFE唔好買，冇用<br />\n寫清楚有齊PFE+BFE+VFE當然最好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ULUsfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ULUsfj.jpg&h=c0ac2f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==阻隔標準==<br />\n歐洲: EN14683 (得BFE，無PFE標準)<br />\n美國: ASTM-F2100 lv 1-3 (3最高)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8AQrM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8AQrM3.png&h=589cbb7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2018 standard)<br />\n<br />\n日本: 日本政府網站提出的VFE測試方法係用~1.7&mu;m嘅濾菌體去測試<br />\n比PFE測試所用粒子要大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqBwecB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqBwecB.jpg&h=6ec9152b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國: KF80/94/99 (99最高)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxcvrLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxcvrLk.png&h=1f22814f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣: CNS14774<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUcy9dF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUcy9dF.png&h=59a4c186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2018 standard)<br />\n<br />\n3M:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ENrv5k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ENrv5k.jpg&h=cb64da11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街邊藥房既口罩<br />\n英文既有ASTM Level就係正版啦<br />\n日文既就睇下有冇BFE+PFE+VFE<br />\n冇上面呢兩樣野是但一樣，或者啲日文/英文錯grammar既100%係假野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==其他類型口罩==<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2549572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2549572&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=094d54a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2549572</a><br />\nN95 -<br />\n1860/1860S/1870屬於醫療用口罩，經NIOSH（美國國家職業安全衛生研究所）認證，亦是FDA（美國食品藥品管理局）批准可用作外科手術口罩，有效阻隔效病毒的飛沫。<br />\n8210/8110/9210屬於工業用口罩，主要用於阻隔塵埃，雖然亦經過NIOSH認證，但沒有FDA認可，未必能有效阻隔飛沫。<br />\nPS 1: 同埋醫護有做fit test,確保冇air leak先戴得, 漏氣既話=冇用, 所以我唔建議一般人買 因為好焗(香港隻NASK就ok既 搭飛機可以用 但貴)<br />\n<br />\n防塵/防花粉口罩 -<br />\n冇用架咪on9啦<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴/其他唔係一次性既口罩<br />\n- 首先你要學識點樣正確除豬嘴<br />\n- 仲要唔知你識唔識洗<br />\n- 唔識洗既會contaminate埋你洗衣機d衫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==產地問題==<br />\n大牌子黎講其實大部分made in china<br />\n因為成本問題，醫管局都好多mic野<br />\n但大廠會有qc，所以quality唔會話爭好多<br />\n<br />\n冇經濟能力，搵唔到既<br />\nMade in china都可以照用<br />\n（用日本黎計made in japan個價係mic 4倍)<br />\n<br />\n邊度有得買？<br />\n去屈人寺,萬寧,donki,cosmo搵下啦<br />\n搵唔到就amazon<br />\n但由於日本野唔送海外 所以自己搞轉運啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==牌子問題==<br />\nRef 1: 香港消委會2017-12口罩測試報告 <a href=\"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/f/article/2256/494_p14-21a.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fechoice.consumer.org.hk%2Ff%2Farticle%2F2256%2F494_p14-21a.pdf&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=3dcc57fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/f/article/2256/494_p14-21a.pdf</a><br />\nRef 2: <a href=\"https://tw.tokyocreative.com/articles/30908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.tokyocreative.com%2Farticles%2F30908&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=891baac4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.tokyocreative.com/articles/30908</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 超立體<br />\n超立體嘅口罩係無鐵線的, 除咗一包七個嗰隻係有nose cut之外, 其他全部都冇, 戴眼鏡有機會會起霧, 但係PFE VFE BFE數據一樣99%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">！！要注意呢隻超立體係唔得嘅！！好多人中伏</span><br />\n呢款超立體只有一層, 除咗呢隻，超立體其他款都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjRLMDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjRLMDd.jpg&h=c5c9e2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面呢隻手術用(サージカルタイプ)資料不詳，冇鐵線，有巴打話係醫療用，亦都有人話唔夠三層，可以嘅話就盡量買返另外嘅款喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vK414pX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvK414pX.jpg&h=f4e4f260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 超快適<br />\n無PFE，得VFE，所以唔係所有款都得<br />\n<br />\n3. 三次元<br />\n日本製，全部Ok<br />\n<br />\n4. BMC<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pgf8RN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pgf8RN.jpg&h=15f6d1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. iris<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uCSUmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uCSUmr.jpg&h=1bb4177a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻冇寫數據 可免則免<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdiR9UV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdiR9UV.jpg&h=f4adf87a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. Made In China<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiO6v5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiO6v5d.jpg&h=609c02b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消委會前幾年test過最好表現，好嘢黎<br />\n不過要注意產地係中國，如果好concern就自行判斷喇<br />\n<br />\n7. <strong>Medicom</strong><br />\n政府醫院都係用medicom ASTM level 1<br />\n<br />\n8. <strong>HALYARD</strong><br />\n可以用，醫療級<br />\n<br />\n9. <strong>誠哥有售</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Htgoyoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtgoyoi.jpg&h=84d7f7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係多人買咗嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">伏嘢</span></span><br />\nFrom 阿里巴巴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aY7CCLq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaY7CCLq.png&h=b52492db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3Q</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3qXCLy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3qXCLy.jpg&h=faa59456&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGn7fxe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGn7fxe.jpg&h=51fa0e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國本土個test都係得kf80<br />\n即係得防塵冇防菌<br />\n佢只係做過bfe test但冇show過數字出黎<br />\n<br />\n韓國隻3Q Premium/Premium Plus係冇喺Ministry of Food and Drug Safety(식품의약품안전처) 取得許可 (의약외품허가Drug Approval System)，佢隻KF80/94就有<br />\n不過有巴打話係大陸公司，但唔肯定係唔係真，呢個大家就自行判斷<br />\n<br />\n隔離post睇到：<br />\n千祈唔好買一款叫救救マスク嘅口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837620\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvATVLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvATVLU.jpg&h=570b0a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國製劣質口罩<br />\n<br />\n因為口罩真係有好多好多牌子，如果以上嘅口罩標纖又無mark，呢個post又無巴絲提起過，個樣又流流地，建議大家買過盒啦，唔好為百幾蚊拎自己條命較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貼森林link請加密<br />\n或者淨係貼網址後面嗰抽number<br />\n唔好益CD-ROM</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"平時用開嘅3M 60926 2097得唔得？"},{"pid":"4d00a9d7c51e989a49035efba4195b58393d1998","tid":1847441,"uid":267535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1481da0b52098bcf243c936694819f2be1ee2d","tid":1847441,"uid":235352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d00a9d7c51e989a49035efba4195b58393d1998","tid":1847441,"uid":267535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls"},{"pid":"779a87d700527f753a2752761c0188311126fdaa","tid":1847441,"uid":241072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"全球瘋搶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b127b8c6cadddfe980853e9a159ee483e49052","tid":1847441,"uid":153764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"現貨得bfe <br />\n照唔照殺"},{"pid":"c70b08ad1460b8743d38ec539acdcbd8674be422","tid":1847441,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit